{"tid":908880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比基尼妹美姿跳冰湖　湖面太硬慘「掰咖」","createTime":"2018-11-20T02:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T02:59:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ad3c5420450a964df325a05db425658347a2ee","tid":908880,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:29:16.000Z","msg":"一名比基尼妹想跳冰湖，但沒想到湖面上的冰太厚，一跳下去不僅沒穿破冰層進水，反而腳扭到「掰咖」。<br />\n <br />\n據匈牙利《Ripost》報導，一名俄羅斯女子在岸上推掉衣服，身穿比基尼泳裝，準備往一旁的冰湖跳下去，待她助跑往湖面一跳時，情況不如預想一般，可以穿破冰層進入冰下的湖水，反而是湖面的冰層太厚，一跳碰到冰面就被彈飛，腳還因此變成「掰咖」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/19/MNgSwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2FMNgSwC.jpg&h=02de45d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/19/a02iBS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F19%2Fa02iBS.jpg&h=88443211&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"550bcda57b99e243078853e5e68cd414f8d681f4","tid":908880,"uid":77813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對腳"},{"pid":"c5712b070b36cf0496dec806cdaf0d65abb9e657","tid":908880,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"比基尼泳裝? 似內衣喎"},{"pid":"a58bb28b8d0b40159719de3cd81f14af9def23e5","tid":908880,"uid":187076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXYsKTE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXYsKTE.png&h=b22ae78c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a601887d64e65594c2c28f0cdc944ba7d5ade0c","tid":908880,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse